      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real-world testing, not sponsored comparisons</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What I Actually Tested</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Same prompt: "consultant website for strategy work"</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Same content: 6 pages, identical copy</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Same customization: logo, colors, images</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Real launch: published both, tracked 6 months</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Conversion tracking: forms, visitors, inquiries</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Designer review quality: documented B12 changes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Real Results Measured</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Time to launch: Mixo 3 hours vs B12 5 days</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Total cost: Mixo $54 vs B12 $180 (6 months)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Visitors: Mixo 1,200 vs B12 1,100</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Conversions: Mixo 34 vs B12 31 inquiries</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Conversion rate: Mixo 2.83% vs B12 2.82%</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Designer changes: spacing, fonts, colors only</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Score Comparison -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Score Comparison</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
