    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-12 bg-[#A855F7]"></div>
        UNEXPECTED FINDINGS
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#A855F7] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üé®</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Designer Changes Were Cosmetic</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">B12's designer didn't rewrite copy or improve conversions. Just spacing, fonts, colors. No strategic value for most businesses.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#A855F7] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚è∞</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Waiting Kills Momentum</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">5-day launch delay meant the consultant pushed back her marketing. Momentum lost. Mixo's instant launch kept energy high.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#A855F7] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üîÑ</div>
